From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kernel-builder <builder@github.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: define MODULE_IMPORT_NS for kernel 4.19

KernelSU requires MODULE_IMPORT_NS which does not exist in kernel 4.19.

Signed-off-by: kernel-builder <builder@github.com>
---
 include/linux/module.h | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

@@ -852,3 +852,4 @@
 #endif	/* CONFIG_MODULE_SIG */
 
 #endif /* _LINUX_MODULE_H */
+#define MODULE_IMPORT_NS(ns)
